00:08:24,256 --> 00:08:25,616
the third person animation set.

154
00:08:28,276 --> 00:08:29,857
So, now we got a character.

155
00:08:31,397 --> 00:08:32,477
But where are we gonna animate it?

156
00:08:32,517 --> 00:08:37,778
Like, we need to understand, like, how to, how to compose art on this kind of canvas,

157
00:08:38,018 --> 00:08:41,139
which is your, your screen, your TV, or your monitor.

