00:09:53,563 --> 00:09:55,843
So, this actually makes it, I mean, for me, this,

181
00:09:56,144 --> 00:09:59,444
this makes it feel like it's a little bit more of an immersive, um,

182
00:10:00,571 --> 00:10:04,255
a real life view of how you would be viewing a world.

